00:04:47.660 --> 00:04:52.120
And those are matter and energy.
So, let's look at what's involved in

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:56.370
each of these,
matter and energy.

00:04:56.370 --> 00:05:00.620
We have to furnish these to the
reaction. And so,

00:05:00.620 --> 00:05:04.870
if we're going to think about energy
