00:07:35.550 --> 00:07:39.990
That's why we're over here talking
about diffusion.

00:07:39.990 --> 00:07:44.440
It's a solid-state process.
So, what we do is pass a form of

00:07:44.440 --> 00:07:48.880
boron over the wafer as the gas
