say, I've got it. I know what's

00:11:29.750 --> 00:11:34.250
going on here.
And so, therefore,

00:11:34.250 --> 00:11:38.750
the model that transformed c into f
of c, x into g of x,

00:11:38.750 --> 00:11:43.250
then underlies the whole
representation.

00:11:43.250 --> 00:11:47.750
And so, the mathematical
formulation of diffusion we owe to

00:11:47.750 --> 00:11:52.660
someone by the name of Adolf Fick.
He was a physician.

00:11:52.660 --> 00:11:57.990
But he loved mathematics.
And, he did to diffusion what

00:11:57.990 --> 00:12:03.330
Balmer did to spectroscopy.
Recall, Balmer studied the

00:12:03.330 --> 00:12:08.660
measurements that were made by
Angstrom. And it was Balmer who fit

00:12:08.660 --> 00:12:13.990
Angstrom's data to that equation
