00:12:13.990 --> 00:12:19.330
concert with the Rydberg Equation.
What Fick did: he looked at Thomas

00:12:19.330 --> 00:12:24.580
Graham's.
Thomas Graham had published some

00:12:24.580 --> 00:12:29.740
diffusion data for the rate of
ingress of some materials into

00:12:29.740 --> 00:12:34.910
aqueous media.
And, Fick was the one who was able

00:12:34.910 --> 00:12:40.080
to fit Thomas Graham's data and give
us a model. And,

00:12:40.080 --> 00:12:45.240
here is, let's jump through here.
This is the cover page. This is

00:12:45.240 --> 00:12:50.410
the first page of the paper.
