00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:35.000
dimensions simultaneously.
The constant of proportionality is

00:14:35.000 --> 00:14:40.000
D, the diffusion coefficient
or diffusivity.

00:14:40.000 --> 00:14:44.000
And, finally, there is a minus sign.
